## Scripts Included

### AD-Discovery.ps1
Collects Active Directory environment information including:
- Domain information
- Trust relationships
- Domain controllers
- Users
- Service accounts
- Privileged accounts
- GPOs
- Security groups
- OUs

### DuplicateAccountsDetection.ps1
Detects duplicate user accounts based on:
- DisplayName
- Email
- EmployeeID
- UserPrincipalName

Exports results to:

C:\ADDiscovery\DuplicateAccounts.csv
